A bachelor’s degree in Computer Science, Applied Mathematics, Economics or in other relevant fields;
Preferably 2+ years of work experience in high growth start-ups, tech companies, consulting or business intelligence;
Fundamental understanding of e-commerce/e-market places and are capable of driving projects to add value to the company;
Strong analytical skills and passion for data; Ability to tell a story from data and present it in a clear and compelling way;
Proficient knowledge of Excel and SQL; Knowledge of VBA or R would be an advantage; Knowledge of Python would be an advantage; Proficient communication in English (Cantonese is a plus); Desire to work in a vibrant and fast-paced environment with high quality standards and tight deadlines;
Great energy and a positive attitude 
What We Offer

Opportunity to take on responsibility from day 1 and have a direct impact on our business & all our customers
A vibrant and international team with diverse background A steep learning curve in e-commerce & entrepreneurship A great collaborative working atmosphere with regular company and team events
Medical Scheme from your very first day Birthday Leave Benefits include free drinks, fresh fruits, amazing coffee and food allowance

